snippet.title: Hannibal gameplay (PC Game, 1992)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Hannibal (aka hannibal: master of the beast), Dos PC game produced by Starbyte Software in 1992 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/hannibal/4065/
Playing through the first turns of this tactical game featuring Carthago and the mediterranean scenario before rise of Rome.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
Steel Panthers 3 - https://youtu.be/R-ySDiT2uFk
Ancient Art of War - https://youtu.be/huAb9i1OSEY
Conflict in Vietnam - https://youtu.be/5wUYrcXDwHA
